---
/* Ecosystem.astro - Sección Dual Target (Sin animaciones de scroll) */
---

<section id="ecosistema" class="ecosystem-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="pill">Plataforma Integral</span>
            <h2>Conectamos <span class="text-gradient">abogados y clientes</span></h2>
            <p class="subtitle">
                Transformamos el modelo tradicional del derecho en una plataforma digital diseñada para potenciar a ambas partes.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cards-wrapper">
            
            <div class="eco-card firm-card">
                <div class="card-glow glow-blue"></div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon-blue"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Para el Estudio Jurídico</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">Herramientas tecnológicas avanzadas para optimizar el trabajo y escalar el volumen de casos.</p>
                    
                    <ul class="eco-features">
                        <li>
                            <span class="bullet"></span>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Automatización Legal</strong>
                                <span>Procesos judiciales y administrativos optimizados mediante tecnología.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="bullet"></span>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Gestión Inteligente</strong>
                                <span>Sistemas diseñados para acelerar la resolución de conflictos legales.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="eco-card client-card">
                <div class="card-glow glow-white"></div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon-white"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Para el Cliente Final</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">Una experiencia digital sin fricciones para que tengan el control y la tranquilidad que buscan.</p>
                    
                    <ul class="eco-features">
                        <li>
                            <span class="bullet-white"></span>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Transparencia Total</strong>
                                <span>El cliente puede ver el estado actualizado de su caso en todo momento.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="bullet-white"></span>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Trazabilidad Digital</strong>
                                <span>Cada etapa y avance queda registrado y accesible en tiempo real.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* --- ESTRUCTURA GENERAL --- */
    .ecosystem-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        background-color: var(--bg-main);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .container {
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* --- HEADER --- */
    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .pill {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem; display: block;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .text-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #94a3b8);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* --- CARDS GRID --- */
    .cards-wrapper {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    /* --- TARJETAS BASE --- */
    .eco-card {
        position: relative;
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        /* Eliminamos opacity: 0 y transform: translateY */
    }

    .eco-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
        border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    }

    /* Resplandores de fondo */
    .card-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.5s;
        z-index: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .glow-blue {
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%);
    }

    .glow-white {
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
    }

    .eco-card:hover .card-glow { opacity: 1; }

    /* --- CONTENIDO TARJETAS --- */
    .card-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
    }

    .icon-wrapper {
        width: 50px; height: 50px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .icon-blue { color: var(--accent); }
    .icon-white { color: var(--text-primary); }

    .eco-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .card-desc {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    /* --- LISTA DE FUNCIONALIDADES --- */
    .eco-features {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0; margin: 0;
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .eco-features li {
        display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .bullet, .bullet-white {
        width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
        margin-top: 8px; flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .bullet { background: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent); }
    .bullet-white { background: var(--text-primary); box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); }

    .eco-features strong {
        display: block; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1.05rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .eco-features span {
        display: block; color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* --- MEDIA QUERIES --- */
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .ecosystem-section { padding: 8rem 0; }
        h2 { font-size: 3rem; }
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
        .cards-wrapper {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .eco-card {
            padding: 3rem;
        }

        .eco-card h3 { font-size: 2rem; }
    }
</style>